5 Oklahoma State Regents for Higher Education;
6 11. 12. "Federal government defense entities" means U.S.
7 Department of Defense installations in the State of Oklahoma
8 including Fort Sill, Tinker Air Force Base, Altus Air Force Base,
9 Vance Air Force Base and McAlester Army Ammunition Plant;
10 12. 13. "For-profit business" means any lawful activity
11 conducted by a business entity with the goal or expectation of
